                    BingX 期現套利雷達 <span class="text-sm bg-indigo-900/80 text-indigo-300 px-2 py-1 rounded border border-indigo-700 ml-2 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(99,102,241,0.5)]">防護罩流動性版</span>
